{"data":[{"name":"100:1","price":"மூச்சிரைக்க அதிவேகமாக ஓடும் குதிரைகள் மீது சத்தியமாக!","arabic":"وَٱلۡعَٰدِيَٰتِ ضَبۡحٗا","category":["100 (Al-Aadiyat)","Al-Aadiyat","Surah Al-Aadiyat"],"ayahNumber":6147,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-ʿādiyāti ḍabḥan ","translations":["By the racers","panting","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-ʿādiyāti","ḍabḥan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1840],[2,1840,2865]]}},{"name":"100:2","price":"இன்னும், (விரைந்து ஓடும்போது தமது லாடங்களால்) தீப்பொறிகளை மூட்டுகின்ற குதிரைகள் மீது சத்தியமாக,","arabic":"فَٱلۡمُورِيَٰتِ قَدۡحٗا","category":["100 (Al-Aadiyat)","Al-Aadiyat","Surah Al-Aadiyat"],"ayahNumber":6148,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"fal-mūriyāti qadḥan ","translations":["And the producers of sparks","striking","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["fal-mūriyāti","qadḥan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1810],[2,1810,2785]]}},{"name":"100:3","price":"இன்னும், அதிகாலையில் (எதிரிகள் மீது) பாய்ந்து தாக்குகின்ற குதிரைகள் மீது சத்தியமாக,","arabic":"فَٱلۡمُغِيرَٰتِ صُبۡحٗا","category":["100 (Al-Aadiyat)","Al-Aadiyat","Surah Al-Aadiyat"],"ayahNumber":6149,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"fal-mughīrāti ṣub'ḥan ","translations":["And the chargers","(at) dawn","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["fal-mughīrāti","ṣub'ḥan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1680],[2,1680,2715]]}},{"name":"100:4","price":"ஆக, அவை அதி(காலையி)ல் புழுதியைக் கிளப்பின.","arabic":"فَأَثَرۡنَ بِهِۦ نَقۡعٗا","category":["100 (Al-Aadiyat)","Al-Aadiyat","Surah Al-Aadiyat"],"ayahNumber":6150,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-atharna bihi naqʿan ","translations":["Then raise","thereby","dust","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-atharna","bihi","naqʿan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1000],[2,1000,1760],[3,1760,2695]]}},{"name":"100:5","price":"ஆக, அதி(காலையி)ல் (எதிரிகளின்) கூட்டத்திற்கு நடுவில் நுழைந்தன.","arabic":"فَوَسَطۡنَ بِهِۦ جَمۡعًا","category":["100 (Al-Aadiyat)","Al-Aadiyat","Surah Al-Aadiyat"],"ayahNumber":6151,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"fawasaṭna bihi jamʿan ","translations":["Then penetrate (in the) center","thereby","collectively","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["fawasaṭna","bihi","jamʿan",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1060],[2,1060,1740],[3,1740,3245]]}},{"name":"100:6","price":"நிச்சயமாக மனிதன் தன் இறைவனுக்கு நன்றி கெட்டவன் ஆவான்.","arabic":"إِنَّ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنَ لِرَبِّهِۦ لَكَنُودٞ","category":["100 (Al-Aadiyat)","Al-Aadiyat","Surah Al-Aadiyat"],"ayahNumber":6152,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"inna al-insāna lirabbihi lakanūdun ","translations":["Indeed","mankind","to his Lord","(is) surely ungrateful","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","al-insāna","lirabbihi","lakanūdun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1170],[2,1170,3420],[3,3420,4730],[4,4730,7605]]}},{"name":"100:7","price":"இன்னும், நிச்சயமாக அவன் அதற்கு சாட்சியாக இருக்கிறான்.","arabic":"وَإِنَّهُۥ عَلَىٰ ذَٰلِكَ لَشَهِيدٞ","category":["100 (Al-Aadiyat)","Al-Aadiyat","Surah Al-Aadiyat"],"ayahNumber":6153,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-innahu ʿalā dhālika lashahīdun ","translations":["And indeed, he","on","that","surely (is) a witness","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-innahu","ʿalā","dhālika","lashahīdun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1950],[2,1950,2630],[3,2630,3560],[4,3560,6685]]}},{"name":"100:8","price":"நிச்சயமாக அவன் செல்வத்தை நேசிப்பதில் கடினமானவன் ஆவான்.","arabic":"وَإِنَّهُۥ لِحُبِّ ٱلۡخَيۡرِ لَشَدِيدٌ","category":["100 (Al-Aadiyat)","Al-Aadiyat","Surah Al-Aadiyat"],"ayahNumber":6154,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-innahu liḥubbi al-khayri lashadīdun ","translations":["And indeed he","in (the) love","(of) wealth","(is) surely intense","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-innahu","liḥubbi","al-khayri","lashadīdun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2090],[2,2090,2930],[3,2930,3840],[4,3840,7055]]}},{"name":"100:9","price":"புதைகுழிகளில் உள்ளவர்கள் எழுப்பப்படும்போது (தன் நிலைமை என்னவாகும் என்பதை மனிதன்) அறியவேண்டாமா?","arabic":"۞ أَفَلَا يَعۡلَمُ إِذَا بُعۡثِرَ مَا فِي ٱلۡقُبُورِ","category":["100 (Al-Aadiyat)","Al-Aadiyat","Surah Al-Aadiyat"],"ayahNumber":6155,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"afalā yaʿlamu idhā buʿ'thira mā fī al-qubūri ","translations":["But does not","he know","when","will be scattered","what","(is) in","the graves","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["afalā","yaʿlamu","idhā","buʿ'thira","mā","fī","al-qubūri",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,910],[2,910,1750],[3,1750,2470],[4,2470,3400],[5,3400,3750],[6,3750,3980],[7,3980,7065]]}},{"name":"100:10","price":"இன்னும், நெஞ்சங்களில் உள்ளவை பிரித்தறியப்படும்போது (தன் நிலைமை என்னவாகும் என்பதை மனிதன்) அறியவேண்டாமா?","arabic":"وَحُصِّلَ مَا فِي ٱلصُّدُورِ","category":["100 (Al-Aadiyat)","Al-Aadiyat","Surah Al-Aadiyat"],"ayahNumber":6156,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"waḥuṣṣila mā fī al-ṣudūri ","translations":["And is made apparent","what","(is) in","the breasts","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["waḥuṣṣila","mā","fī","al-ṣudūri",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1120],[2,1120,1530],[3,1530,1730],[4,1730,4815]]}},{"name":"100:11","price":"நிச்சயமாக அவர்களுடைய இறைவன் அந்நாளில் அவர்களை ஆழ்ந்தறிபவன் ஆவான்.","arabic":"إِنَّ رَبَّهُم بِهِمۡ يَوۡمَئِذٖ لَّخَبِيرُۢ","category":["100 (Al-Aadiyat)","Al-Aadiyat","Surah Al-Aadiyat"],"ayahNumber":6157,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"inna rabbahum bihim yawma-idhin lakhabīrun ","translations":["Indeed","their Lord","about them","that Day","(is) surely All-Aware","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","rabbahum","bihim","yawma-idhin","lakhabīrun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1310],[2,1310,3300],[3,3300,3900],[4,3900,5100],[5,5100,8715]]}}],"chapter":["100 (Al-Aadiyat)","Al-Aadiyat","Surah Al-Aadiyat","Chapter Al-Aadiyat","Aadiyat","Surah Aadiyat","Chapter Aadiyat","Al Aadiyat","Surah Al Aadiyat","Chapter Al Aa